      • getSourceType

        public java.lang.String getSourceType()
        Gets the sourceType. The source that this credentials object connects to. - `box` indicates the credentials are used to connect an instance of Enterprise Box. - `salesforce` indicates the credentials are used to connect to Salesforce. - `sharepoint` indicates the credentials are used to connect to Microsoft SharePoint Online. - `web_crawl` indicates the credentials are used to perform a web crawl.
        Returns:
        the sourceType
